Example Midlets 

This is the starting point for accessing the documentation for example MIDlets.

Each example has a set project files for building from the command line and various integrated development environments.

See the instructions for building from the command line and also instructions for building and runinng using IDEs.

The MIDlets are supplied with Java™ documentation including design diagrams

IAPInfoMIDlet
        IAP Info API example is in the directory S60MIDPExamples\IAPInfoMIDlet

eSWTMIDlet
        eSWT API example is in the directory S60MIDPExamples\eSWTMIDlet

SystemProperties
        SystemProperty API example is in the directory S60MIDPExamples\SystemProperties
